What's up?

44:19.691 --> 44:21.492
Ryan Winter.

44:21.526 --> 44:24.229
Yeah.
What about him?

44:24.262 --> 44:25.797
Well, I don't have
any details yet, just --

44:25.831 --> 44:27.298
he called the office.

44:27.332 --> 44:29.667
He was asking for somebody
to come out to his house.

44:29.701 --> 44:31.136
And it probably
should be my boss,

44:31.169 --> 44:32.670
but my boss is in Tahoe.

44:32.704 --> 44:34.139
Come out to his house?
For what?

44:34.172 --> 44:36.307
He just said that he needed
to talk to somebody.

44:36.341 --> 44:38.910
About the things
that he's done.

44:38.944 --> 44:40.178
Now, obviously,
I said that I'd go.

44:40.211 --> 44:41.880
I'm rolling out there now.

44:41.913 --> 44:43.849
I thought I'd give you the heads
up in case you wanted to come.

44:43.882 --> 44:46.184
-You fucking serious?
-Well, nothing's official,

44:46.217 --> 44:49.254
but if this is what it
sounds like it could be...

44:49.287 --> 44:50.688
you deserve to be there, man.

44:50.722 --> 44:52.423
I mean,
you, of all people.

44:52.457 --> 44:54.359
You're the best, Frank.
I'm on my way.

